    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>Implemented as a special derivative of block stack, that looks after multiple
types of tracked items (LCL, Containers, cars...). will need to be able to differentiate
between the different types of tracked items held within it, and to
group and display appropriately.</text>
